            <li>
                The 7th term of the given AP is: 1/a , (1/a + 1), (1/a + 2),…. ?
                <div class="options">
                    a) 1/a + 6<br>
                    b) 1/a + 7<br>
                    c) 1/a + 8<br>
                    d) 1/a + 7/7
                </div>
